  "description": [
    "EDITORIAL PAGE Vol BNo 141 THE MILWAUKEE LEADER Published every evening except Sunday by the Milwaukee Social Democratic Publishing Company at Chestnut and Sixth Streets VICTOR L BERGER Editor On indefinite leave of absence and not responsible for the contents of t s Pper Associate Editors E H THOMAS JOHN M WORK OSCAR AMERINGER SUBSCRIPTION RATESThe mail edition of The Milwaukee Leader will bp sent to any subscriber in the United States under 3rd class postage for cents per month 190 for three months 380 for six months 760 for one year The Home Edition will be delivered in Milwaukee and suburbs for 10c a week r 40c a month If the delivery of your paper is not regular notify the circulation depart ment Grand 6060 immediately and your complaint will be promptly attended to Office Honrs 8 a m to 6 p m r Tel Grand 5060 AS TO THE INTERNATIONAL James Onealthe only one of the three American delegates to the international Socialist congress at Berne who went abroad has returned But his report has not as yet been recved The passport difficulties made it impossible for him to start to Europe until long after the congress adjourned"
